OL,3,C'Cruel clause' writes thousands out of
OL,4,Cinquiry and redress bill
OL,6,FStormont has been urged to remove a
OL,7,F"cruel clause" that "writes out"
OL,8,Fthousands of women, girls and their
OL,9,Fchildren in a mother and baby homes
OL,10,FBill.
OL,12,FCampaigners, including survivors of
OL,13,Fthe homes run by the Catholic Church,
OL,14,Freligious orders, some Protestant
OL,15,Fdenominations as well as the state,
OL,16,Fand relatives, gathered at Parliament
OL,17,FBuildings on Monday.
