OL,3,C'Cruel clause' writes thousands out of
OL,4,Cinquiry and redress bill
OL,6,FMore than 14,000 women and girls are
OL,7,Fthought to have passed through the
OL,8,Finstitutions, with many found to have
OL,9,Fbeen mistreated, held against their
OL,10,Fwill and forced to give up their
OL,11,Fchildren for adoption.
OL,13,FThe Inquiry (Mother and Baby
OL,14,FInstitutions, Magdalene Laundries and
OL,15,FWorkhouses) and Redress Scheme Bill
OL,16,Fwas introduced at the Assembly earlier
OL,17,Fthis year, and is being scrutinised by
OL,18,Fthe Executive Office Committee.
