OL,3,C'Cruel clause' writes thousands out of
OL,4,Cinquiry and redress bill
OL,6,FThe Bill is to establish a statutory
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry and a statutory redress
OL,8,Fscheme, with a payment of #10,000 to
OL,9,Fbe made to eligible claimants, and a
OL,10,F#2,000 payment to eligible family
OL,11,Fmembers on behalf of a loved one who
OL,12,Fhas died since September 29 2011.
OL,14,FAdele Johnston, of Birthmothers and
OL,15,Ftheir Children Together, described the
OL,16,F2011 cut-off date as "cruel".
