OL,6,F"On one hand we are pleased we have
OL,7,Ffinally got as far as the legislation
OL,8,Fbeing written but there needs to be a
OL,9,Flot of work done to make it acceptable
OL,10,Fto victims and survivors," she said.
OL,12,F"There are a lot of aspects that need
OL,13,Fto be discussed and hopefully amended.
OL,15,F"We are quite hopeful going forward,
OL,16,Fbut it all depends on their decisions
OL,17,Fat the end of the day.
