OL,4,Cinquiry and redress bill
OL,6,F"It's been a long, long campaign, and
OL,7,Fa long, hard campaign, jumping through
OL,8,Fhoops, meeting ministers, baring our
OL,9,Fsouls to the public. It's not easy.
OL,11,F"But with one cruel clause in the
OL,12,FBill, they have written out thousands
OL,13,Fof women, girls and their children.
OL,15,F"The 2011 date for posthumous claims
OL,16,Fis utterly unacceptable and we will
OL,17,Fcontinue to fight that."
OL,19,FRoisin and Lisa Morris were among
OL,20,Fthose who attended Stormont on Monday.
