OL,6,FTheir mother Madeline Morris was sent
OL,7,Fto the Marianville Mother and Baby
OL,8,FHome on the Ormeau Road in south
OL,9,FBelfast when she was 18, after
OL,10,Fbecoming pregnant, and forced to give
OL,11,Fher baby up for adoption.
OL,13,FMrs Morris died in 1992, and the Bill
OL,14,Fas it is currently written will not
OL,15,Frecognise her.
OL,17,F"That's why we're here today," Roisin
OL,18,FMorris said, adding that they had not
OL,19,Ffound out what happened to their
OL,20,Fmother until her first child came
OL,21,Fsearching for her last year.
